{"tid":728401,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"波台有C朗迷出假ＰＯＳＴ，我身為C朗迷感到羞恥，特此出帖以正視聽","createTime":"2018-07-03T18:46:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T19:46:22.000Z","uid":173160,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eb7e8dba8dc0eb50064cdd626cfc0af849156ea9","tid":728401,"uid":173160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T18:46:25.000Z","msg":"睇得出有班盲目既C朗迷真係玻璃心，我地衰左咪衰左囉！又唔係衰唔起<br />\n根本唔洗出假ＰＯＳＴ屈其他人既，依家咁樣做顯得我地C朗迷冇品，實在唔要得！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假ＰＯＳＴ　ＬＩＮＫ：<br />\n鳩硬冇親戚<br />\n5 日前<br />\n16強小數據，帶波過人美斯3次，C朗5次<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/724595/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/724595/page/1</a><br />\n實際數據<br />\nＣ朗５射１中關鍵傳球１次<br />\n<a href=\"http://bf.win007.com/Count/1483046cn.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbf.win007.com%2FCount%2F1483046cn.htm&d=3fAmrUDp82qBK%2BHFr%2BGhvARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=39aacd7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bf.win007.com/Count/1483046cn.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n係美斯係廢，我地Ｃ朗表現更廢。<br />\nＣ朗５射１中關鍵傳球１次<br />\n<br />\n兩個人一齊登機，冇必要出假ＰＯＳＴ老屈！<br />\n超愈唔到美Ｃ咪超愈唔到美Ｃ囉，Ｃ朗在我地心中永遠都係第一架啦，<br />\n我唔希望有個別會員開假ＰＯＳＴ，搞到我地Ｃ朗迷乞人憎<br />\n我希望你地唔好因個別球迷對Ｃ朗反感，我依家企出黎以正視聽，<br />\n訟謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我現在代表Ｃ朗迷美Ｃ迷道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e3cdab255670776fc0747687524978d3695acd","tid":728401,"uid":3548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T18:58:02.000Z","msg":"收皮啦美斯狗"},{"pid":"ed12292d751c62fc0faa98cef3c01674e222740d","tid":728401,"uid":173160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21e3cdab255670776fc0747687524978d3695acd","tid":728401,"uid":3548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T18:58:02.000Z","msg":"收皮啦美斯狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T18:59